Introduction:
This project is a student progress tracker app whic is using the tkinter in python

Features:
Add-delete-manage student data
you can add multiple subject for each student
this system calculate student and school averages
this system has sorting system and filtrenig (search ) system
this system has motplotlib it is create pie chart and graph

Installation:
To run the app locally:
1. Make sure Python 3.x is installed.
2. Install required dependencies:
   pip install matplotlib

How to Run the App:
1. Open terminal/command prompt in the project folder.
2. Run the main script:
   python main.py

App Elements:
- Element 1: Main screen navigate interface with buttons for all features
- Element 2: pop up screen used for input (adding students,grafes,attandence)
- Element 3: student table display all student with Id -average grade - attendance - subject

Libraries Used:
- [Tkinter] – For creating screen 
- [Json] – for data
- [Matplotlib] – for data visualization


Project Structure:
ProjectFolder/
├── students.json            # Stores student data
├── main.py              # Main application logic and GUI implementation
├── README.md            # Project documentation

Testing:
Include test scenarios covering:
Valid Cases:
- Adding a new student with a valid ID
- Entering grades between 0–100
- Setting attendance between 0–100
- Viewing charts with existing data
Invalid Cases:
- Entering empty student ID
- Using non-alphanumeric student IDs
- Entering non-numeric grades or attendance
- Accessing non-existing students
Example Scenarios:
- Adding a student twice shows an error
- Invalid input does not crash the program
- Charts do not open if no data exists
- Table updates dynamically with search and sort

